Output docs/assets/ompconf-skills.gif
Require bun
Set Shell "bash"
Set FontSize 24
Set Width 1360
Set Height 920
Set Theme "Dracula"
Set Padding 8
Set TypingSpeed 1ms
Hide
Type "bun src/cli.ts tui --home demo/fixtures/home --cwd demo/fixtures/home/workspace/example-project --state-dir demo/fixtures/home/.ompconf --screen skills"
Enter
Sleep 900ms
Show
Sleep 900ms
Hide
Type "q"
Sleep 200ms
